Package com.pb.sawdust.calculator

Provides classes dealing with calculations and functions.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CollapsibleFunction
    The CollapsibleFunction interface specifies a function whose number of arguments may be reduced because some of their values are known.
    Function1<X,Y>
    The Function1 class represents a one-argument function.
    Function2<X,Y,Z>
    The Function2 class represents a two-argument function.
    NumericResultFunction1<T>
    The NumericResultFunction1 specifies a one-argument function which returns a numeric value as its result.
    NumericResultFunction2<X,Y>
    The NumericResultFunction2 specifies a two-argument function which returns a numeric value as its result.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DegenerateFunction1<X>
    The DegenerateFunction1 provides a single argument function which simply returns its argument.
    NumericFunction0
    The NumericFunction0 abstract class is used to specify zero-argument functions.
    NumericFunction0.FlexFunction0
    The FlexFunction0 provides a skeletal implementation of NumericFunction0.
    NumericFunction1
    The NumericFunction1 abstract class is used to specify functions which take one number as an argument and return a number.
    NumericFunction1.DecimalFunction1
    The DecimalFunction1 class provides a FlexFunction1 which acts on decimals.
    NumericFunction1.FlexFunction1
    The FlexFunction1 provides a skeletal implementation of NumericFunction1.
    NumericFunction1.IntegralFunction1
    The IntegralFunction1 class provides a FlexFunction1 which acts on integers.
    NumericFunction2
    The NumericFunction2 class is used to specify functions which take two numbers as arguments and return a number.
    NumericFunction2.DecimalFunction2
    The DecimalFunction2 class provides a FlexFunction2 which acts on decimals.
    NumericFunction2.FlexFunction2
    The FlexFunction1 provides a skeletal implementation of NumericFunction2.
    NumericFunction2.IntegralFunction2
    The IntegralFunction2 class provides a FlexFunction2 which acts on integers.
    NumericFunctionN
    The NumericFunctionN abstract class is used to specify functions which take one or more numbers as an argument and return a number.
    NumericFunctionN.DecimalFunctionN
    The DecimalFunctionN class provides a FlexFunctionN which acts on decimals.
    NumericFunctionN.FlexFunctionN
    The FlexFunctionN provides a skeletal implementation of NumericFunctionN.
    NumericFunctionN.IntegralFunctionN
    The IntegralFunctionN class provides a FlexFunctionN which acts on integers.
    NumericFunctions
    The NumericFunctions class contains interfaces and methods related to numerical functions.
    NumericValuesProvider
    The NumericValuesProvider class provides a structure for getting primitive numeric argument values for use in numeric functions.
    NumericValuesProvider.ByteArrayValuesProvider
    The ByteArrayValuesProvider class provides a numeric values provider which holds its values in a byte array.
    NumericValuesProvider.ByteValuesProvider
    The ByteValuesProvider provides a structure for a numeric values provider which naturally holds bytes.
    NumericValuesProvider.DoubleArrayValuesProvider
    The DoubleArrayValuesProvider class provides a numeric values provider which holds its values in a double array.
    NumericValuesProvider.DoubleValuesProvider
    The DoubleValuesProvider provides a structure for a numeric values provider which naturally holds doubles.
    NumericValuesProvider.FloatArrayValuesProvider
    The FloatArrayValuesProvider class provides a numeric values provider which holds its values in a float array.
    NumericValuesProvider.FloatValuesProvider
    The FloatValuesProvider provides a structure for a numeric values provider which naturally holds floats.
    NumericValuesProvider.IntArrayValuesProvider
    The IntArrayValuesProvider class provides a numeric values provider which holds its values in an int array.
    NumericValuesProvider.IntValuesProvider
    The IntValuesProvider provides a structure for a numeric values provider which naturally holds ints.
    NumericValuesProvider.LongArrayValuesProvider
    The LongArrayValuesProvider class provides a numeric values provider which holds its values in a long array.
    NumericValuesProvider.LongValuesProvider
    The LongValuesProvider provides a structure for a numeric values provider which naturally holds longs.
    NumericValuesProvider.ShortArrayValuesProvider
    The ShortArrayValuesProvider class provides a numeric values provider which holds its values in a short array.
    NumericValuesProvider.ShortValuesProvider
    The ShortValuesProvider provides a structure for a numeric values provider which naturally holds shorts.
    PartialNumericFunctionN
    The PartialNumericFunctionN class provides a numeric function in which some arguments have be pre-specified.
    SimpleCollapsibleFunction
    The SimpleCollapsibleFunction class provides a simple, shell implementation of the CollapsibleFunction interface.
